Package: rgl2gltf
Type: Package
Title: Read and write .gltf and .glb files
Version: 0.1.6
Author: Duncan Murdoch
Maintainer: Duncan Murdoch <murdoch.duncan@gmail.com>
Description: GLtf is a format for 3D models.  This package adds
 read and write functions to it.
